{{ill|Takagi District, Hizen Province|ja|高木郡}}, {{ill|Hizen Province|ja|肥前国}} (referenced in the "Fukae Family Documents," designated an Important Cultural Property of Saga Prefecture, March 16, 1987). * The '''Ōno Clan''' was also a surname of the {{ill|Xianbei|ja|鮮卑}} or {{ill|Gaoche|ja|高車}} peoples. It was granted to {{ill|Li Hu|ja|李虎}} by Emperor {{ill|Xiaowen of Northern Wei|ja|北魏の孝文帝}}.
== See also == * {{ill|Ōno Castle|ja|大野城}}
{{Aimai}}
