renced in the "Fukae Family Documents," designated an Important Cultural Property of Saga Prefecture, March 16, 1987). * The '''Ōno Clan''' was also a surname of the [[:en:Xianbei|Xianbei]] or [[:en:Kang-chü|Gaoche]] peoples. It was granted to [[:en:Li Hu (general)|Li Hu]] by Emperor {{ill|Xiaowen of Northern Wei|ja|北魏の孝文帝|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xiaowen of Northern Wei|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}.
